column1: # Supplementary Dataset S13. This tab delmited table contains the results of the aseQTL linkage results of the 4133 antisense traits at 5% FDR.
# This tab delmited table is the results of the aseQTL linkage results
# of the 4133 antisense traits at 5% FDR. Each row correspond
# to one linkage between a target antisense trait and its aseQTL. When
# a trait was linked to more several locus correlated more than 0.8
# we considered that it corresponded to a single QTL, which position
# could not be determined. they were regroup.
# Here each row correpond to a group and the different location
# of the grouped QTL are separated with coma.
# First field is the name of antisense trait (target)
# Next 3 fields are the coordiante of the QTL as a
# genomic interval.  Note that each QTL is considered
# as spanning in between the first non linked variant.
# last field is an indicater of whether the linkage correspong to
# a cis or a trans linakge
